Bjond:<br>
<br>
If you solo alot, you might think about putting some alternate advancement points into Bind Wound.  With even one point in it; you can bind up to 60%, which really makes a difference when you solo.  I put three points into Bind Wound and can now bind to 80%; this really helps out when soloing since I am starting at 80% rather than 50%.  Although you can throw points into increased stamina, I think you get hps for soloing by putting them into Bind Wound.<br>
